{
  "name": "Prone Lab \u2014 stand up, crawl, and attacking a prone target (C5)",
  "description": "Ship-readiness bench for the C5 prone movement penalty. The Brave Crawler starts prone: open Tactics to Stand Up (spends half your speed and clears prone), or stay down and crawl (every hex costs double, and you attack at disadvantage). Valeria can melee the Prone Dummy (advantage) or throw a javelin at it (disadvantage). Shove a goblin to knock IT prone too. The Dummy has 0 speed so it stays down.",
